Name: valico
License File: LICENSE
Description: JSON Schema validator and JSON DSL

* What is this crate used for?
Validating JSON values against a JSON Schema, and performing JSON coercion.

* Are there any use restrictions? i.e. only for development hosts
No.

* What differs from upstream? Include a changelog if feasible.
Modified build-dependency `phf_codegen` version from `"0.11.1"` to `"0.14.0"`.

* Are there any restrictions to how it should be rolled?
Keep build-dependency on `phf_codegen` updated to match the tree-wide `phf` version.

* Is there anything else which makes this dependency "special"?
No.
